               Sunshine          Irradiation 
                                 (10[.sup]4[/] 
                                 kilocalories/square 
                                 meter) 

I              2,800-3,300       670-840                   Northern 
                                                           Ningxia, 
                                                           northern Gansu, 
                                                           southeastern 
                                                           Xinjiang, 
                                                           western Qinghai, 
                                                           western Tibet 

